":"She makes every day a BIG adventure.\nLike the time we had to get out of a murukku maze.\n“I know! Let’s eat our way out,” Ameera said.","words":[[192,"She"],[193,"makes"],[194,"every"],[195,"day"],[196,"a"],[197,"BIG"],[198,"adventure."],[199,"Like"],[200,"the"],[201,"time"],[202,"we"],[203,"had"],[204,"to"],[205,"get"],[206,"out"],[207,"of"],[208,"a"],[209,"murukku"],[210,"maze."],[211,"“I"],[212,"know!"],[213,"Let’s"],[214,"eat"],[215,"our"],[216,"way"],[217,"out,”"],[218,"Ameera"],[219,"said."]]},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/80905/size6/20324b57a8a703eb1d3d9999550f037e.jpg","text":"Like Ameera said, we’re a team.","words":[[220,"Like"],[221,"Ameera"],[222,"said,"],[223,"we’re"],[224,"a"],[225,"team."]]}],"stats":{"pages":11,"words":225}}